Package: arkg
Title: Access to the ArKG Chile Archaeological Dating Knowledge Graph
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Victor", "Mendez", email = "victor.mendez@uc.cl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Client for the Archaeology Knowledge Graph of Chile (ArKG,
    <https://arkg.cl>), providing access to Chilean archaeological dates
    (radiocarbon and thermoluminescence) via its SPARQL endpoint powered
    by 'MillenniumDB'.
License: CC BY-SA 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://arkg.cl, https://github.com/ArKG-Data/arkg-r
BugReports: https://github.com/ArKG-Data/arkg-r/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
